Anna Rijnders (Hannah Hoekstra) sluit zich helemaal af in de wereld van apps en sociale

mysterious App that starts to terrorize her, distributing compromising photographs, videos
and text messages about herself and delves deeper and deeper into her personal life,
flawlessly exposing all of her deepest secrets.
